Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:02.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた空　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:07.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,広がる夢 未来のドアを開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:15.01,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光に絶えず今も照らされてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鮮やかな空　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:29.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窓を開ければ注ぐSunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:36.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に触れたら　昨日の涙も消えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:43.63,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しくなっていつも見えない星を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:53.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すぐ側にあると気つかず追い求めていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:57.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見上げた空広がる夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:01.02,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来のドアを開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:07.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光に絶えず今も照らされてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:11.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空には瞬く夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:15.14,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数え切れぬ願いが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:21.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今叶う時を待ち焦がれてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:26.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:02.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望浩瀚星空　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:07.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限延伸的梦想 开启通往未来的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:15.01,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的光芒照亮此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有明亮色彩的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:29.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推开窗便是满眼阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:36.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微风拂过 风干昨日的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:43.63,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞时总爱寻找那颗看不见的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:53.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味追逐寻觅却从未发现它近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:57.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望浩瀚星空　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:01.02,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限延伸的梦想 开启通往未来的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:07.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的光芒照亮此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:11.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚星空中闪耀的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:15.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怀揣着数不尽的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:21.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已无心等待它们慢慢实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:26.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:29.50,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}心までは奪えない　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:35.03,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}何度でも何度でも　駆け出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.86,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}風とともにヒュルリラヒュルリラ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.77,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}颯爽と近づくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:56.90,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}暇つぶしのつもりでいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:23:00.43,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}ちょっと本気見せてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.44,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}モノクロの世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:08.36,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}君だって飽き飽きしてるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:12.02,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}汚されても手放せない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:18.64,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}たったひとつのプライド抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:22.53,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}夢は夢で終われない 君は君のままで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:26.25,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}いつだって生まれ変われる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:31.12,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}うつつ抜かすくらいの狂おしいスリルこそが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.47,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}愛を救う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:36.32,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}心までは奪えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.00,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}誰にも壊せない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:42.44,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}迷惑はかけるモノでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.11,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}叫び続けていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:49.59,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}何度でも何度でも駆け出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:54.78,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}欲しいのは時代の1ページ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:29.50,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}永不失我心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.55,0:22:35.03,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}无数次无数次 奔跑朝前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.86,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}伴随清风摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:52.77,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}亲近飒爽心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:56.90,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}若只是打发无聊的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:23:00.43,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}也请稍微拿出点干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.44,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}这枯燥无味的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:08.36,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}你也一定感到厌倦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:12.02,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}即使障碍重重也绝不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:18.64,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}紧拥唯一的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:22.53,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}梦想不会终结 你也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:26.25,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}何时都能重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:31.12,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}只有超越现实般疯狂的紧张感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.47,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}才能拯救爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:36.32,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}永不失我心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.00,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}谁都无法阻挡我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:42.44,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}忧愁总是自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.11,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}想要高声呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:49.59,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}无数次无数次 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:54.78,edc00,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2}想在时代中书写自己的一页篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡斯克的宝宝不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经离巢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.09,0:01:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经长成大人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ok It's safe！（安全了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了塔科特君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊 是多亏了你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君真是直爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我初登舞台的对象是塔科特君 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要练习一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有点想上厕所……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二班的小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说今早上又在禁断的星球进行她的野鸟观察呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁断的星球？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是男厕所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在男厕所里进行观察啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 那个女孩 她在随心所欲地生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs28\be1\blur4}第十五话 封印的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(南十字渡口)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特酱在学艺会上的接吻对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}学艺会：中小学生文艺技能表演活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和子酱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为塔科特君可是相当的受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野只是像对乌鸦和副部长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我很有趣而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特酱还真是受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没明白这是怎么回事……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特酱还真是不懂女人心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和子酱这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新藤家的小少爷要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你两个建议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是像之前说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你成为我作画的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是你绝对应该成为我作画的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这就是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为此而生的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星十字团第一队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor（皇帝）代表的位置正虚席以待你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无论何时都会做好迎接你的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是想在这儿使用「王之柱」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能总是有它的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是神赐予的东西对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有战士的印记 换句话说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有巨大的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说「野心」也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为战士的Driver们都赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 刻在你胸膛上的不是战士的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是王的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快我就会把那位银河美少年打败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我从没想过要夺走他的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说 我是把他当做同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤野？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:05:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个……阿姨 我想找你借点儿钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚 我听阿姨说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回不回来 跟我们没关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是像平时一样 聊点儿有趣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是关于水野喜欢的人的话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于卡斯克的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定比喜欢卡斯克还要喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那……就是关于副部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:07:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定比喜欢副部长还要喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔科特君的确很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道鞠野也对塔科特君……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论何时都站在水野这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀 没我跟着就什么事都做不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Banishing Age的Star Driver们终于齐聚一堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manticole最终还是没有踏进过这房间一步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要感谢她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她通过Eingott之眼 为我们找到了日死之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 她说没有找到是在撒谎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长说谎的女孩子 真是可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩带伞了没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动之后还叫我参加武术的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点太过度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的你这是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你的气势还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真拿你们俩没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伞能遮得住三个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子选一个你喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下一次的练习要下一个赌注
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌注？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你赢了 我与和子的婚约即作废
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你都可以待在那伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啥……我该怎么吐槽才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开的那个玩笑 我可要当真了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊塔科特君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来塔科特君对和子……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:11:09.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:09.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点感冒那也是没办法的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要请假的话也该事先联络一下我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你是巫女这件事被暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是有点不舒服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那件事 能够隐瞒多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以永远瞒下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎话说久了 就会变成事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 由谎言构成的世界却非常梦幻美好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半身 区分 目标男性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会消逝的梦幻即为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野你在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧 快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半身 区分 目标男性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半身 区分 目标男性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半身 区分 目标男性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半身 区分 目标男性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 要见见她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说分开了也没什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但与她见一面把一切都说清楚不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是不是真的抛弃了自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好地确认一次 无法朝前迈进不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你真的是想见她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是「真的」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么鞠野非得了解我真实的感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为你是姐姐 就好像对我了如指掌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 为什么事到如今还要回到岛上来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为你是姐姐 就好像对我了如指掌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了 全都是因为那家伙回来的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚出海的海螺哦 要来点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃啊 不过下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去本岛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野 对你说了很过分的话 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我有点失常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的是光想到那个人在这里 我就会失常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那个人在岛上期间我决定离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算等那个人离开后就马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:15:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P.S.仔细想一下我是第一次去本岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很是兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鞠……野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚出海的海螺哦 要来点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是类似预知梦之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是……怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水……？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(南十字码头)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去本岛买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以载我一程吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反搭讪最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}反搭讪 即为女生向男生搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 是头一次去本岛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在安全驾驶的条件下飞速航行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野 身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 暖下身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是稍微休息下比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次握紧我的手好么……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子现在真的在这里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是梦吧 这是现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经分不清楚了……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早上开始岛上的空气就蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才到这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想离开这个岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 和子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是祭祀的时间 这可是巫女的职责啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巫女的职责？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:20:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说今天早上开始 结界的躁动一直很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 别客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是些粗茶淡饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是日死之巫女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到今天为止 都没有想过要离开岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子是巫女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 不能从岛上离开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事你是什么时候知道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小时候便知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也有着巫女的职责吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛上的四方巫女拥有着很强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要时刻牢记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有别人知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野……姐姐和奶奶 其他人都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无用 明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后要是发生了什么 直接来这里商量就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢清爽的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风再次带来热浪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数千遍的轮回 数万遍的闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育出光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的歌曲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开岛屿的方法 让我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日死之巫女小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管有些突然 Star Driver Quiz
